description:
This video focuses on the "Hard Space Bop Book" of Sun Ra compositions and the music is "Oo-la-wee". The recordings come from the original master tape and sound far better than the version released on Atavistic Records. The songs include "Dark, Outer Space, Velvet and Ankhnation (Ankhnaton).

NOTE: There is some noticeable distortion and noise picked up by the microphone which was laying directly on the tape deck until someone moved it.
